                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" id="arnold_sng_2" hclass="sense" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" htag="span" hclass="sensetop"><span class="def" hclass="def" htag="span">(1921-2006) a British <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/composer#composer_topg_1" title="composer definition"><span class="ndv">composer</span></a> who wrote several <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/symphony#symphony_topg_1" title="symphonies definition"><span class="ndv">symphonies</span></a>, as well as music for <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/ballet#ballet_topg_1" title="ballets definition"><span class="ndv">ballets</span></a> and films. He was made a <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/knight_1" title="knight definition"><span class="ndv">knight</span></a> in 1993.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
